# gpSP UART joypad macro, version 1
# ROM: p.gba, direct SPI-mmap boot
# Original record start: 24790 emulated frames after retro_reset().
# Events 0..88 and 136..219 retain captured frame numbers.
# Events 89..135 were B transitions whose UART frame numbers were truncated;
# they are reconstructed uniformly over captured frames 4865..8740.
# Load while paused with:
#   uart_debug_client.py --commands-file p_gba_map_replay.macro
